- Lab 4ct GIA D-VVS1 Ideal Cushion Modified: **[$7,412](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/25222994?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
- Natural 4ct GIA F-VS1 Ideal Cushion Modified: **[$85,685](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28281344?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**

**→ The best entry point** for lab buyers is the [GIA 4ct D-VVS1 Ideal Cushion Modified at $7,412](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/25222994?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — GIA certification carries maximum resale and insurance recognition, D colour is absolute top, VVS1 is genuinely clean, and the $7,412 price point makes a 4ct cushion accessible in a way that no natural 4ct stone can match. For natural buyers who have specifically examined and committed to natural origin at this size: the [GIA 4.04ct F-VS1 Ideal at $85,685](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28281344?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the only natural 4ct cushion entry point worth considering — and it may not be in stock when you look.

